Biodose Tools Contributors

The project is initially developed by RENEB association, as a collaboration between Universitat Autònoma de Barcelona (UAB), Bundesamt für Strahlenschutz (BfS), Durham University (DU), Institut de Radioprotection et de Sûreté Nucléaire (IRSN), Universidad de la Rioja (UdR), and Public Health England (PHE).
